data.description: Check out this one of a kind home close to interstate, Ft Campbell, Restaurants and entertainment.Custom counters and cabinets in the kitchen & master bedroom, Also a large moveable Island with lots of storage. Stainless steel appliances. The living room has vaulted ceiling, gas fireplace, custom mantle. Laundry room with half bath. 3 nice sized bedrooms and formal dining room. All one level.The full unfinished basement has room for growth.Property includes full concrete driveway with back access to 2 car garage.Dog friendly fenced back yard.Private back yard.From the large front porch to the basement potential this home is a must see.
